11:52.679 --> 11:54.179
Okay...

11:54.181 --> 11:56.381
This night is going great.

11:56.383 --> 11:58.216
Okay.

12:01.455 --> 12:04.289
Hm... do I want to go
to Chez Fancy Pants,

12:04.291 --> 12:07.926
